<li id="cite_note-LibérationObit-4">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Lib%C3%A9rationObit_4-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Lib%C3%A9rationObit_4-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Lib%C3%A9rationObit_4-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Lib%C3%A9rationObit_4-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Lib%C3%A9rationObit_4-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFPaquot2018" class="citation news cs1 cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source">Paquot, Thierry (1 October 2018). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.liberation.fr/debats/2018/10/01/sophie-body-gendrot-au-dela-des-villes_1682348/">"Sophie Body-Gendrot, au-delà des villes"</a> [Sophie Body-Gendrot, beyond the cities]. <i><a href="/wiki/Lib%C3%A9ration" title="Libération">Libération</a></i> (in French). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220124155211/https://www.liberation.fr/debats/2018/10/01/sophie-body-gendrot-au-dela-des-villes_1682348/">Archived</a> from the original on 24 January 2022<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">20 August</span> 2022</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Lib%C3%A9ration&amp;rft.atitle=Sophie+Body-Gendrot%2C+au-del%C3%A0+des+villes&amp;rft.date=2018-10-01&amp;rft.aulast=Paquot&amp;rft.aufirst=Thierry&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liberation.fr%2Fdebats%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2Fsophie-body-gendrot-au-dela-des-villes_1682348%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASophie+Body-Gendrot" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-PS2019-5">
